You’ve been planning this trip for months and it is finally here. Family needed a bit of convincing but they let you and your friends go for this 5 day trip. The details have been meticulously planned and you’ve been packing for almost a month. The day before the trip you go through your suitcase and your Travel Blue Folding 12 L Backpack to make sure you haven’t missed anything. After the checks are done off you go.

After school most of your friends are scattered in different colleges across the country. Although everyone tries their best to keep in touch it is not always easy. After a few months of coordination and planning this trip has been possible. 2 of your friends are taking their cars and one of them honks at your gate for pick up. You hug your parents put the suitcase in the boot and toss in your Travel Blue backpack in the backseat. There are a few more pick ups but this unisex Travel Blue backpack only measures 90 x 150 x 35 mm in dimension and doesn’t take up a lot of room. Weighing only 80 g this Travel Blue backpack ensures that it doesn’t add to the luggage weight.

Whenever you travel you always go for luggage that can handle a bumpy ride and clumsy handling. This Travel Blue backpack is made of polyester which is resilient and fits the bill perfectly. Once you reach the resort you have your luggage sent up to the room. A few of you decide to go on a small walk along the lake that runs through the resort. Take your backpack as it comes with adjustable shoulder straps which ensure that your back and shoulders don’t have to bear a huge strain. Besides you have many things to carry around that you can’t put in your suitcase such as toiletries itinerary snug jacket and other such essentials. Fortunately this 12 litre backpack from Travel Blue can easily hold all this and more. Apart from all this the folding feature of this backpack makes it a handy travelling accessory.
